ia

Class Genetic

  • java.lang.Object
    • ia.Genetic

  • public class Genetic
extends java.lang.Object
    The class managing any approach for the Genetic algorithm. Its main field is the population which is an array of Individuals. It can run no matter the DNA implementation chosen for the Individuals.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Genetic

        public Genetic(Game game,
               int sizePop,
               java.lang.Class<? extends DNA> dnaImpl,
               Selection selector,
               double mutationAtZero,
               boolean decrease,
               int framesPerAction)
        Main Genetic Constructor. Initializes his attributes based on the inputs given.
        Parameters:
        game - the game to play on. The values of whale and obstacle are passed by reference.
        sizePop - the size of the population to apply the algorithm on
        dnaImpl - the Class to use as the implementation of DNA for the Individuals of the population.
        selector - the selection method to use to select the next generation
        framesPerAction - the number of frames per action allowed to the AI chosen by the user
